data.description: READY TO MOVE IN! Fresh Paint all rooms. Over 1900 sq ft in this lovely 3/2/2. Oversized garage has additional work area including a FULL bath and fully floored attic. Fridge/W/D included. Large Kitchen/breakfast/laundry and separate formal area w/wet bar. Elegant French doors from master lead to a private secret garden and have its own patio. Roof,AC,Heat,Water Htr,Auto Garage Door Opener, Trash Compactor, Electric pnl replaced. Fishing/boating/rec.9 int. lakes,3 pools, major golf course.
